  <h2 class="docs-section-header">HTML</h2>

  <p>HTML should be written as clear and semantically as possible. Keep from nesting <code>divs</code> too deeply.</p>
  <p>Write html components as self contained modules for easy re-use and flexability.</p>
  <div class="code">
  {{#markdown}}
  ```html
  <div class="block block--modifier">
    <div class="block__element">
      <p>...</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  ```
  {{/markdown}}
